trans-unit.source: Provides data for the <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigated" /> event.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona datos para el evento <see cref="E:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigated" />.

trans-unit.source: Handle the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigated?displayProperty=nameWithType> event to receive notification when the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control has navigated to a new document.
trans-unit.target: Controlar la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigated?displayProperty=nameWithType> eventos para recibir una notificación cuando el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> ha navegado hasta un nuevo documento.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatedEventArgs> object passed to the event handler lets you retrieve the location of the new document through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatedEventArgs.Url%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatedEventArgs> objeto que se pasa al controlador de eventos le permite recuperar la ubicación del documento nuevo mediante el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowserNavigatedEventArgs.Url%2A> propiedad.

trans-unit.source: When the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigated?displayProperty=nameWithType> event occurs, the new document has begun loading, which means you can access some of its content through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> property.
trans-unit.target: Cuando el <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigated?displayProperty=nameWithType> evento tiene lugar, el nuevo documento ha empezado a cargar, lo que significa que puede tener acceso a parte de su contenido a través de la <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, o <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> propiedad.
